WEBVTT FILE:

00:00:00.850 --> 00:00:05.240
obviously becoming a parent stressful and requires time both to take care

00:00:05.240 --> 00:00:09.640
 of your spouse because they're gonna be down and just going through

00:00:09.640 --> 00:00:14.030
 childbirth and spending time with your new child or baby. So I think

00:00:14.030 --> 00:00:18.430
 communication with your chain of command is first and foremost.

00:00:18.430 --> 00:00:22.820
 I don't know any leader who would not want to give their sailor or

00:00:22.820 --> 00:00:27.210
 Marine an opportunity to spend time with their family, but also understand

00:00:27.210 --> 00:00:31.610
 that there are sometimes limitations where you are in a location

00:00:31.610 --> 00:00:36.000
 where you can't necessarily make it back. And so having those, um,

00:00:36.000 --> 00:00:40.400
 those conditions with your family back home to make sure that they're

00:00:40.400 --> 00:00:44.790
 taking care of is also an important feature.

